{"tid":1594710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇反對跳閘既人，本身係日日跳閘?","createTime":"2019-09-25T16:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T18:49:36.000Z","uid":92459,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"157cc4f640a55c459dfe6d0ec249fb600d9ab982","tid":1594710,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"見到隔籬post既人話跳閘冇用。<br />\n又有人話從來都唔同意跳閘。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得話罷搭/2蚊飛/長者卡都冇問題<br />\n但係好多人本身都唔跳，然後又阻止人跳，之後又話效益低。<br />\n<br />\n本身講全民跳閘，結果10個都冇1個跳。<br />\n明明係因為少人參與，所以先危險，少人參與所以效益低，根本就係應該令更多參與，從而減低風險，增加效益。<br />\n黨鐵就係靠車費賺錢，想問下唔俾錢都話冇用，咁咩先有用?<br />\n加上成日都話睇完環境再決定跳唔跳，又唔係叫你一定要跳。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好多人本身都冇跳閘，但係就不斷叫人唔好跳。<br />\n最後，想問有冇人係本身日日都跳閘，但係而家係反對跳閘?"},{"pid":"07dbc4b2ed26f39549348db43ea0712b1a4a2c04","tid":1594710,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b9ff0ee584d7600077a9c4b62baaf555e813811a","tid":1594710,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:36:53.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2fbe93e1d77e0d61cf884e6e3d42085139b09fe9","tid":1594710,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5e883a16951eb79fae177758dcb7f8d7b8b734a8","tid":1594710,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:38:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3f00b9b5cac8dc8a288efc0206520956b80fb4e4","tid":1594710,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:40:19.000Z","msg":"［香港獨立！唯一岀路！］<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【警世】不要再執迷於追求五大訴求<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594691</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6MVGwi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6MVGwi.jpg&h=1ed93f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWKL3KV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai